<section id="about" class="section-padding bg-light-bg">
  <div class="container-custom">
    <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-12 items-center">
      <div class="lg:pr-10">
        <h2 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-black text-primary mb-6">Our Heritage: Building Trust Since Day One</h2>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-6">
          Spot-On Inspectorate is more than just a service; we are your advocates in the complex world of home construction.
          With <b>decades of experience</b> in Singapore's home renovation industry, working closely with town councils and technical bodies, we bring a level of expertise that is unmatched in the field.
        </p>
        <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed mb-8">
          We understand that a home is your most significant investment. Our mission is to ensure that every Singaporean homeowner can move into their property with total confidence, knowing that every tile, pipe, and wire has been professionally vetted.
        </p>
      </div>
      
      <div class="relative flex justify-center items-center lg:pl-10">
        <div class="relative z-10 p-6 bg-white rounded-3xl shadow-xl border border-gray-100 max-w-sm lg:max-w-md mx-auto">
          <img src="/img/about/radac.png" alt="RADAC Certified Member" class="w-full h-auto rounded-lg" />
        </div>
        <div class="absolute inset-0 border-8 border-secondary rounded-3xl -m-4 transform rotate-2"></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
